node.text:
Repost from @PaulWalkerFdn:⁣
⁣
“There’s a time and place for everything, but as I get older, I like finding those human moments and really connecting.” - #PaulWalker ⁣
⁣
What it’s all about. #DoGood ⁣
⁣
Photo by @bbirtell

node.text: Did you know #IntoTheBlue is available to stream on @Showtime? What’s your favorite scene from the deep diving adventure starring Paul and @JessicaAlba? 🌊 #FBF #TeamPW

node.text: Remembering our dear Paul today. We miss you and will forever have you in our hearts. ✨💙 #HBD #TeamPW

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Paul Walker on September 05, 2021 tagging @meadowwalker, and @paulwalkerfdn. May be an image of 3 people, child and people standing.

node.text: Today is #InternationalDayOfCharity and we want to highlight the #PaulWalkerFoundation, which was started by his daughter @meadowwalker. Paul always had a love for helping people, giving back, and doing good. On this day, we motivate you to #DoGood and give back to a charity that is special to you.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Paul Walker on August 27, 2021 tagging @aleciarodriguez_inc. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text: How cool is this digital piece by @aleciarodriguez_inc?! Be sure to keep sharing your amazing work using #PaulWalkerArt so we can continue to feature new artists for #FanArtFriday! #TeamPW

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Paul Walker on August 19, 2021 tagging @paulwalkerfdn. May be a black-and-white image of 1 person.

node.text:
“Life’s most persistent and urgent question is, ‘what are you doing for others?’” - Martin Luther King Jr.⁣
⁣
In honor of #WorldHumanitarianDay and Paul’s legacy, we encourage you to #DoGood, whether that be supporting the @paulwalkerfdn or another cause you’re passionate about. ⁣
⁣
#TeamPW
